quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  50,16,"Gom…óii Men tagii ne…ó…óanke on, Me…óen anndi ko wonkii makko kin sowinsinirta mo. Ko Menen …ìuri …ìadaade mo e dii …óa…óol (makko) daande ngol"
  50,17,"tuma nde ja…ì…ìoytoo…ìe …ìen …ói…óo ja…ì…ìoroytoo [golle makko …óen] √±aamo e nano, hara hi…ìe joo…óii"
  50,18,"O wowlataa konngol, si wanaa hino takko makko winndoowo tawaa…óo"
  50,19,"∆äe…ó…óere maayde nden ardi e goonga : \"Ko …óum wonunoo ko dogayno…óaa"
  50,20,Wuttee ka alaandu ; ko nden woni √ëalaande kammbaa nden
  50,21,"Wonkii kala ara, hara hiki wonndi e soggoowo e seedotoo…óo"
  50,22,Gom…óii a laatinoke welsindii…óo e ndee. Men hunci wirngallo maa ngon kisan; gite maa …óen hannde ko see…ìu…óe
  50,23,"Wonndii…óo makko on wi'a: \"Ko …óum …óoo woni ka am …óoo, maandinaa-…óum"
  50,24,"Bugee ka Jahannama onon …ói…óo, kala yeddu…óo canndallo"
  50,25,"ha…óoowo mo∆¥∆¥ere, jaggitoowo, sikkitii…óo"
  50,26,on wa…óidu…óo e Allah rewetee…óo goo. Bugee mo ka nder lepte sa…ótu…óe
  50,27,"Cinndadiijo makko (seytaane) on wi'i: \"Joomi amen, mi bewinaali oo; si ko woni, ko e majjere wo…ó…óunde o wonunoo e mun"
  50,28,"[Allah] daala : \"Wata on yeddondir ka Am …óoo ! Nde tawnoo Mi ardiniino e mon kammbaa"
  50,29,Konngol wa…ótitetaake ka Am …óoo ; Mi siforaa kadi too√±oowo jeyaa…ìe …ìen